Description:
After the defeat of the Great Bird, a portal similar to the one that brought you here appears nearby, and you all feel compelled to cross it. 

The conflict within Tulah is evident, as she hesitates over whether to cross the rift with you or not. It is a decision she must make on her own. Just as you are about to reach the breach, Tulah rushes through it before you do. It seems she has decided to help you in your world as you helped her in hers!
DescriptionAction: That is how your adventure in the past ends.
